        "content": "## Borek Finance — Outlook ingest (Docker Compose)\n\n1. Import with `docker compose --profile n8n up -d`\n2. **Outlook New Email** — select Microsoft Outlook credential\n3. **Header Auth** credential `Borek Finance email ingest` (`X-Email-Ingest-Key`)\n4. API URL is `http://backend:8000` on the Compose network\n5. Optional env: `OUTLOOK_FOLDER` (default Inbox)",
